# Demo terminal recording
Output demo.gif

# Setup the terminal
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"

# Recording commands
Type "echo 'Welcome to VHS!'" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "ls -la" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "echo 'This is a terminal recording created with VHS'" Sleep 500ms Enter  
Sleep 2s
Type "date" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 1s